name: Telluric planet #1
description:
This little planet may be dull-looking, but it is nonetheless a miracle: accreted matter thanks to favourable gravitational fields, leading to a planet. Its lack of atmosphere makes it improper to the development of any lifeform.
It is a common piece of the Celestial OBJKT collection, encapsulated in its customised container.

40 seconds animation, 1200 frames (1500 x 1500 pixels).
